{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_02_02",
  "title": "白石千紗 2話 いろんな形",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～ん、助けて下さい～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ help me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、千紗。何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s up‚ Chisa? Something the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "例のユニットのメンバー四人で\n初めてレッスンをしたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The four members for the one-off team\nhad our first lesson together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "初回だから一人ずつ自己紹介することになって\n私は遙子さんの真似をして名前と年齢を言ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We started out by introducing ourselves.\nI tried to copy Haruko-san‚ saying my name and age.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "白石千紗、十七歳です、って……\nそしたらこころちゃんに怒られちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa Shiraishi‚ 17. Like that.\nBut that just got Kokoro-chan mad with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "こころとキャラがかぶるので止めて下さい\nって言われました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Don't do that to overlap Kokoro's character!\"\nShe said that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばこころはいつも言ってるな\nみんなのこころを鷲掴み、赤崎こころ十四歳です、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s Kokoro’s bit‚ isn’t it?\nShe is like “Kokoro-chan Akazaki‚ 14‚ here to grab your heart!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "それで私、あたふたしちゃって\nそこからはうまく喋れなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That completely threw me off my game.\nI lost my ability to speak.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "最年長の私がみんなを引っ張らなきゃいけないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the oldest. I’m supposed to take the lead…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで初レッスンはどうなったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How did the actual lesson go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんが仕切ったり提案したりしてくれて\nレッスンは無事に終わりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro-chan led us through it and made suggestions.\nIt went well‚ in the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "最初はみんなぎこちなかったけど\nこころちゃんのトークで和んで明るくなったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were a little awkward to start with‚\nbut Kokoro-chan's talk set a friendly mood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "私はこころちゃんみたいに出来なかったんです\n私の方がお姉さんなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t do it. But Kokoro-chan could.\nEven I’m the onee-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それで、このままじゃいけないと思って\n思い切ってこころちゃんに聞いてみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew I needed to make a change‚\nso I took the plunge and asked Kokoro-chan about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなのお姉さんになりたいんだけど\nどうしたらいいのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told her I want to be the onee-chan in the group‚\nand I asked her how I can do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "年下のこころにそれを聞いたのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You asked Kokoro? But she’s younger than you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "そしたらこころちゃんが教えてくれたんです\n腹筋を毎日千回やればみんなついてきてくれるよって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s when Kokoro-chan gave me the secret.\nEveryone will follow me if I do 1000 sit-ups a day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "それで昨日は一人でずっと腹筋をしてたんですけど\nお腹が筋肉痛になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I did sit-ups non-stop yesterday.\nAnd now my tummy hurts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こころの言うことは鵜呑みにしない方がいいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn’t listen too much of Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "でもこころちゃんは本当に凄いんです\nムードメーカーで、存在感があって、いつも前向きで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kokoro-chan really is amazing.\nShe’s a mood-maker‚ has a strong presence and so cheerful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "レッスン中もこころちゃんが盛り上げて\n私達を引っ張ってくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She got us all fired up for the lesson\nand took the lead in getting us through it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "あたふたして何も出来なかった私とは大違いです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meanwhile‚ I could barely get a word out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まだ一回目のレッスンだ。そこまで考えなくても……\n千紗はこれから頑張ればいいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was only the first lesson. No need to overthink it.\nKeep trying your best‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どれだけ私が頑張っても\n年上らしく振る舞えるかどうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure if I can act like a onee-chan‚\nno matter how hard I try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "きっと出来るさ\n千紗はもっと自分に自信を持っていいと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet you can.\nYou need to have more confidence in yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "自分に自信……そうですよね\n私でもみんなのお姉さんになれますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Confidence in myself… Maybe you’re right.\nMaybe even someone like me can become everyone’s onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "いくらこころちゃんが凄いからって\n全部任せきりはダメですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know Kokoro-chan is incredible‚\nbut I can’t expect her to handle everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "最年長の私がもっとしっかりしないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the oldest. I need to get my act together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの真似をして失敗したので\n次はお姉ちゃんを参考にしてみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I failed by trying to copy Haruko-san.\nNext‚ I’ll draw on my own onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "私がみんなのお姉さんになれるように\nもう少し頑張ってみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to be the onee-chan.\nI’ll keep trying a little longer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
