    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりダメでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope. I knew I couldn’t do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "心が折れるのが早いな……。今度は何があったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You sure do give up quickly. What happened this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "あれから何度か四人でレッスンしたんですけど\n前向きなすずちゃんが積極的に動いて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve had a few more lessons together.\nSuzu-chan is so cheerful and active.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "しっかり者のすみれちゃんがフォローして\n明るくて元気なこころちゃんが盛り上げて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan is reliable and always backs everyone up.\nAnd Kokoro-chan is bright‚ energic‚ and she livens everything up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "私がいなくてもみんなちゃんと出来ていて\n私の出る幕がないんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone is doing fine without me‚\nand they don’t need my help at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "個性の強い三人だからな\n年上でもこの三人をまとめるのは大変だと思うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re three individuals with highly unique personalities.\nI doubt it’ll be easy for anyone to take the lead in that group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お姉ちゃんならもっとうまくやれたと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure my sister could do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに私がどんなに頑張っても\nお姉ちゃんみたいに出来る気がしなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it feels like I can’t be like her‚\nno matter how hard I try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
