      "text": "……この間、麻奈さんのバースデーパーティーで\n琴乃ちゃんが麻奈さんの話をしてましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the birthday party for Mana-san‚\nKotono-chan talked about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんのようになろうと思って頑張ったけど\n麻奈さんみたいには出来なかったって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said she tries to be like Mana-san‚\nbut she can’t quite do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.1666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 259.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "お姉さんのようになれなくて\n琴乃ちゃんは辛かったんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It must have been hard for Kotono-chan‚\nnot feeling like she can match up to her onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs033.m4a",
      "text": "今の私みたいな気持ちだったんでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that’s what I’m feeling now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.3333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 270.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "年上はなんでも出来ると千紗は思ってるようだが\nそんなことはないからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem to think being older means you can do everything.\nThat’s simply not true‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.03333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈だってなんでも出来た訳じゃない\n千紗と同じように悩んだり苦しんだりしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even Mana-san couldn't do everything.\nShe struggled and suffered just like you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.6666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 282.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs034.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？\n麻奈さんはなんでもうまく出来た人\nじゃないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She did?\nI thought Mana-san could do\npretty much anything‚ to be honest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 292.46666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
