      "text": "麻奈だって思い通りにいかないことは沢山あったさ\nだからなんでも出来るお姉さんにならなくていいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She had lots of things that didn’t work out for her.\nYou don’t need to become some kind of all-powerful onee-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.46666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "沙季や麻奈のようになれなくても\n千紗は千紗らしいお姉さんになればいいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t try to be like Saki or Mana.\nJust be yourself. Your version of a “onee-chan.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.53333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 302.03333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs035.m4a",
      "text": "私らしいお姉さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My version…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.03333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 304.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "例えば上に立って引っ張っていくんじゃなくて\n隣に並んで一緒に歩く姉がいてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to be the one pulling them up.\nWhy not stand alongside them and walk together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.6666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 312.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_02-chs036.m4a",
      "text": "上に立つだけが姉じゃない……\nそうですね、{user}さんの言う通りです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s another way to be a onee-chan.\nYes. I think you’re right‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
